---
source: tests/cli.rs
expression: help
---
Inspect and manage requests

Usage: requests <COMMAND>

Commands:
  list     List pending requests involving the active account
  create   Create a request immediately
  accept   Accept an incoming request after authoritative validation and confirmation
  decline  Decline an incoming request without sending money
  info     Show information about one open request
  help     Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help
          Print help
